name: Life Organizer
description: Life Organizer is a mobile web app that I currently have in development. This application is designed to solve a few inconveniences I have with my current management apps. I wanted to create something that would contain all the information I use for task tracking in programming and development. I will be using a React stack for this project. The app will be released in steps that you can see by going to the milestones sections of its GitHub repository.
